10. SOFTWARE & FIRMWARE

10.1 Core Software Stack

Layer Technology Function
Real-time OS FreeRTOS Hardware abstraction, task scheduling
Beamforming Library Custom C++ with ARM NEON SIMD Phased array calculations
Communication Stack LWIP + MQTT Network connectivity
Safety Monitor Independent watchdog + BIST Continuous self-test
Configuration JSON-based with versioning System parameters

10.2 Key Algorithms

Algorithm Purpose Performance
Time-Reversal Mirror Focus optimization < 5 iterations to converge
Adaptive Impedance Matching Efficiency optimization > 95% matching efficiency
Obstacle Avoidance Beam reformatting < 50 ms detection and reformat
MPPT (Maximum Power Point Tracking) Receiver optimization 99% tracking efficiency
Multi-user Scheduling TDMA/FDMA resource allocation 85% channel utilization

10.3 API Specifications

```python
# Example Python API Call
import aetherlink_api

# Initialize connection
system = aetherlink_api.connect(ip="192.168.1.100")

# Configure beam to receiver at coordinates
system.configure_beam(
    target_id="receiver_001",
    power_level=2.5,  # Watts
    frequency=250000,  # Hz
    beam_width=5.0     # degrees
)

# Monitor system status
status = system.get_status()
print(f"Efficiency: {status.efficiency:.1f}%")
print(f"Beam temperature: {status.temperature:.1f}°C")
```

